{Speech 4}{}{Время:60000 Нет ответа:Завершить диалог / Close dialog}
{Speech 5}{}{Oh, what did you want?}
{Speech 5 Answer 6}{}{You know, I'm looking for pre-war programs on facial plastic surgery}
{Speech 6}{}{What the devil could they be needed for now? [glances at you] Then again, none of my business. I've seen something like that in the archives[glances again] Hmm. Fine. I'll give you access to this information. But only to this. God help you.}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit}{}{Thank you so much. I'll never forget it.}
{Speech 7}{}{It's you again? What do you need?}
{Speech 7 Answer 8}{}{Oh, I lost the disk. Can I make a copy one more time?\n}
{Speech 7 Answer 9}{}{Oh, I lost the disk. Can I make a copy one more time?}
{Speech 8}{}{Fine. You women are always losing everything.}
{Speech 8 Answer Exit}{}{Thank you very much\n}
{Speech 9}{}{You women are always losing everything... Not now, I'm too busy. You can try tomorrow.}
{Speech 9 Answer Exit}{}{Damn it!}
